  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Streamer Destiny is a pioneer in the streaming world. Love him or hate him, with a career spanning over a decade he has built one of the most dedicated communities in the industry. DGG, the Daliban, his followers have many names and the memes in the community are too many to count.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >DGGWare is a collection of meme based micro games in the vein of WarioWare. Like Destiny's stream it covers topics from gaming, politics, philosophy, debate, art, culture and drama.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Friends and foes make their appearances. It's a game for newcomers as well as memers from the old guard. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Don't let memes be dreams.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Features</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fast-paced reaction based gameplay</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >65 micro games based on community memes </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Leaderboard for healthy competition</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Additional art by Gemzar</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Yee</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pepe</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Streamer Destiny is a pioneer in the streaming world. Love him or hate him, with a career spanning over a decade he has built one of the most dedicated communities in the industry. DGG, the Daliban, his followers have many names and the memes in the community are too many to count.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >DGGWare is a collection of meme based micro games in the vein of WarioWare. Like Destiny's stream it covers topics from gaming, politics, philosophy, debate, art, culture and drama.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Friends and foes make their appearances. It's a game for newcomers as well as memers from the old guard. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Don't let memes be dreams.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Features</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fast-paced reaction based gameplay</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >65 micro games based on community memes </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Leaderboard for healthy competition</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Additional art by Gemzar</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Yee</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pepe</p></li></ul>",
